Package emr_vis_nlp.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MainModel
    Interface which should be implemented by all classes seeking to act as the model in the MVC design pattern for the emr-vis-nlp system.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Document
    Represents a single unit of data (ie, records for 1 patient, single arguing document, etc.).
    NullMainModel
    Empty model for use when no dataset is loaded.
    PredictionCertaintyTuple
    Tuple representing back-end prediction and associated certainty for a given attribute.
    TextInstance
    Smallest textual unit composing a given Document.
